    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        All adults hospitalized to have one of the following major surgery: resection of
        oeso-gastric, intestinal and pancreatic cancer, treatment of intra-abdominal aortic
        aneurysm, coronary artery bypass graft, endarterectomy, hip fracture prosthesis

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hospitalization &lt;24 hours

          -  Absence of surgical procedure

